  "title": "为什么懂营销的 PM，更容易做出好产品？丨 Supra Insider",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk5MDkxNDU4Nw==&mid=2247485245&idx=1&sn=8796ae261e312ee03835f0162ea0760c",
  "date": "2026-01-20 12:46:00",
